query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(mi_idx t mc) NoMergeJoin(mc mi_idx t mi) NoMergeJoin(mc mi mi_idx t mk) */ select count(*)
from title AS t
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2009 AND mi_idx.info_type_id = 101
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info_type_id = 8
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id;
